Python code to check:
def calc_check_digit(number):
    """Calculate the check digit."""
    check = sum(((i % 9) + 1) * int(n)
                for i, n in enumerate(number[:-1])) % 11
    if check == 10:
        check = sum((((i + 2) % 9) + 1) * int(n)
                    for i, n in enumerate(number[:-1])) % 11
    return str(check % 10)
